         <para number='1' comment='work/workboard/job/cargo/haul'>
         What you do to earn a living in the game varies from rank to rank. New players haul cargo around the Solar System. Cargo jobs are offered on the workboard - type 'WORK' to see the jobs currently available. You can be notified whenever new jobs are posted onto the workboard by typing 'JOBS ON' - turn the notifications off again with 'JOBS OFF'.
