         Planet-owners can move money from their personal bank account to the planet treasury, with the command 'TRANSFER megagroats' or 'XFER megagroats', where 'megagroats' is the number of meg to be transferred. There is no limit on the amount you can transfer in one go. The transfer is taxed at the very high rate of one third.
